{
  "stem": "12904.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I got my first assignment to Schick General Hospital in Iowa-- Clinton, Iowa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I was sent there, I think it was-- I got my papers in September, I think, '43.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took me longer than it should have because I had moved around and I had to have letters of reference from everywhere I had been.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I signed up and it was, I think, January that I was sent to Clinton, Iowa.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after I was there for about a year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I established an occupational therapy department.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of my friends had been sent to eastern hospitals, eastern army hospitals, and so I asked the Surgeon General's office if I could be sent to one of the eastern hospitals.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got my orders, 16-- I don't know how you-- you know how to say in triplicate, but I don't know-- it was 16 copies-- that I was sent to Walla Walla, Washington.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was east of the Pacific Ocean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's why-- that's one of the reasons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I had no idea where it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had to find out and so on, but that's where I was assigned so I went.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then when that closed, at the end of the war I was sent to Fort Lewis, Washington.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had opened a department at Walla Walla, McCaw General Hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Fort Lewis there were already were one or two departments.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had a convalescence handle, they had a general hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a big place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was there, stayed there until 1949 as an occupational therapist.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
